          <w:szCs w:val="22"/>
        </w:rPr>
        <w:t xml:space="preserve"> button beside it) moves between stages. Each stage unlocks one more block of the model. The order follows the course syllabus, not Blanchard&#x2019;s chapter order — the open economy is introduced before the Phillips curve.</w:t>
      </w:r>
